column5: ....I know you're hanging round the puter when you ought to be looking after Liam so I thought I'd give you a little peak.

ok... thats just not right... showing my "rod" off to the masses like that...  I like my pr0n kept personal... and that my friend is pr0n!! She's a beaut Chris!!  Now... to get my grubby hands on her....    Gerritt.
That's just an awesome pic Chris, looks like it was taken for a catalogue or something...  rod looks great!!
